{"tid":297531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔下一代是否有機會脫貧？","createTime":"2017-06-25T14:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T10:47:14.000Z","uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b3f0543f59548d01d0a509d5544bdd6e03c81f","tid":297531,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"大家成日都話窮人之所以窮<br />\n除左無家底<br />\n仲因爲貧窮父母所灌輸既窮人思想導致<br />\n咁上連登大家睇野多左<br />\n知道中產有錢佬大概會點由細教育仔女<br />\n或者至少知道邊d係窮人思維唔應該傳比下一代<br />\n咁計落連登仔至少會俾一般人有更正確既教育下一代既思想<br />\n咁係咪代表連登仔既下一代有機會上流？<br />\n先唔好講咩無女有咩下一代呢d廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf925b1f2991e2d1ef268f5f9fb9a29eda429279","tid":297531,"uid":68736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"撚有下一代咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0a3b2d67766e8d685d924b98ee77fb2a81d367","tid":297531,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"有腦嘅根本唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ec52dc081f84847617322c7b5e51094cfcbb59","tid":297531,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚有下一代咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勿講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3949389bcc5e1ee3be5277b67a066038a81e749","tid":297531,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有腦嘅根本唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有正確觀念<br />\n能否改變資源不足階級複製既命運？"},{"pid":"36fb95d5c54e299ffbc528d331236f76f30a0efd","tid":297531,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{